(a)$100 000 for a contravention of any of the following sections of the Forest Planning and Practices Regulation: 4.63 (2); 35 (3); 36 (1) or (2); 37; 38; 44 (1) (b) or (2); 45 (2); 46.1 (2); 46.2 (5); 54; 56 (1), (2) or (3); 57; 59; 60 (1) or (2); 61; 62 (1) (b) or (2); 106.2 (1);

