(e)$5 000 for a contravention of any of the following sections of the Range Planning and Practices Regulation: 40 (1); 41 (1); 42 (2) (a) or (b); 46 (a), (b) or (c).

[am. B.C. Regs. 226/2006, s. 4; 163/2023, Sch. 1, s. 1; 62/2024, Sch., s. 12.]

Penalties — Woodlot Licence Planning and Practices Regulation
